Name: Tink C++
URL: https://github.com/tink-crypto/tink-cc
Revision: c687dd86fbfd231f194114d0d86d0e3c9b02c92d
License: Apache-2.0
License File: src/LICENSE
Security Critical: yes

Description:
  Tink is a multi-language, cross-platform, open-source library that provides
  cryptographic APIs that are secure, easy to use correctly, and hard to misuse.
  This repo is the dedicated C++ implementation. It will replace the C++
  components previously sourced from the mono-repo at //third_party/tink.

Local Modifications:
  None
